ed in the compositional process.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 4agenre. 4amusic. 4amusicians. 4aopera music. 4ascore. 4asymphonic music. 7aMUSIC / Genres & Styles / Classical.2bisacsh1 aJohnson, Douglas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTyson, Alan, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aWinter, Robert, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Package Archive Pre-2000z97831106353480 cprintz978052032415240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052032416940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520324169423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520324169/original  a978-3-11-063534-8  University of California Press Package Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles